    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:1.2",
          "pli": "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya. ",
          "en": "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:1.3",
          "pli": "Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ passāmi sakkārena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ. ",
          "en": "Take a case where I see a certain person whose mind is overcome and overwhelmed by honor. When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:1.4",
          "pli": "Idha panāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ passāmi asakkārena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ. ",
          "en": "Take another case where I see a certain person whose mind is overcome and overwhelmed by lack of honor. When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:1.5",
          "pli": "Idha panāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ passāmi sakkārena ca asakkārena ca tadubhayena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ. ",
          "en": "And take another case where I see a certain person whose mind is overcome and overwhelmed by both honor and lack of honor. When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:1.6",
          "pli": "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … ",
          "en": "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:1.7",
          "pli": "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:2.1",
          "pli": "Idamavoca bhagavā. ",
          "en": "That is what the Buddha said. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:2.2",
          "pli": "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: ",
          "en": "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:3.1",
          "pli": "“Yassa sakkariyamānassa, ",
          "en": "“Whether they’re honored "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:3.2",
          "pli": "asakkārena cūbhayaṃ; ",
          "en": "or not honored, or both, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:3.3",
          "pli": "Samādhi na vikampati, ",
          "en": "their immersion doesn’t waver "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:3.4",
          "pli": "appamāṇavihārino. ",
          "en": "as they live diligently. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:4.1",
          "pli": "Taṃ jhāyinaṃ sātatikaṃ, ",
          "en": "They persistently practice absorption "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:4.2",
          "pli": "sukhumaṃ diṭṭhivipassakaṃ; ",
          "en": "with subtle view and discernment. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:4.3",
          "pli": "Upādānakkhayārāmaṃ, ",
          "en": "Rejoicing in the ending of grasping, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:4.4",
          "pli": "āhu sappuriso itī”ti. ",
          "en": "they’re said to be a good person.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:4.5",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:4.6",
          "pli": "Paṭhamo vaggo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:5.1",
          "pli": "Dāruṇo baḷisaṃ kummaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:5.2",
          "pli": "dīghalomi ca mīḷhakaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:5.3",
          "pli": "Asani diddhaṃ siṅgālaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.10:5.4",
          "pli": "verambhena sagāthakanti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
